No, when I talk about finding a partner and happiness, I'm talking about my fellow incels. I myself, I'm asexual because I cannot believe in the falsehood of "love" after knowing the true barbarism of human nature. To me, happiness is simply the elimination of suffering. My suffering is my hideous face and only surgery can heal me. If I had a 10/10 loyal virgin gf who loved me, I would still probably off myself because her vagina and affection wouldn't be able to fix my face.

&#x200B;

I also don't identify as incel. If I was an incel, I'd be much happier and I'd only need an amount of surgery that is obtainable before it's too late. I'm a truecel, I'm so ugly that you would pull a gun out and shoot me if you saw my face.
